0working%20with%20me%20over%20all%20these%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20spent%20more%20than%20nine%20years%20working%20together%20at%20DeepMind.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20Hassabis%20acted%20as%20the%20company's%20public%20face%20and%20CEO%2C%20largely%20leading%20the%20company's%20high-profile%20acquisition%20deal%20with%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Schmidt%2C%20Google's%20CEO%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20acquisition%2C%20last%20year%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90959853%2Fmustafa-suleyman-inflection-pi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFast%20Company%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehe%20only%20got%20to%20know%20Suleyman%20after%20spending%20considerable%20time%20with%20Hassabis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20understand%20at%20the%20time%20how%20good%20a%20technologist%20he%20was%20because%20Demis%20sort%20of%20overwhelmed%20him%20in%20that%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20sort%20of%20in%20Demis's%20shadow%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20he's%20emerged%20from%20that%20shadow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20DeepMind%2C%20Suleyman%20was%20initially%20chief%20product%20officer%20and%20later%20head%20of%20applied%20AI.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20finally%20joined%20DeepMind's%20parent%20company%2C%20Google%2C%20as%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20AI%20product%20management%20and%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Suleyman's%20attempt%20to%20step%20decisively%20out%20of%20Hassabis's%20shadow%20came%20when%20he%20left%20Google%20and%20cofounded%20Inflection%20AI%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20years%20later%2C%20Inflection%20was%20bought%20by%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Suleyman%20was%20installed%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232927c18-31e2-41dc-9451-3a35602e219d%5C%22%3E'Pretty%20relentless'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESuleyman's%20time%20at%20DeepMind%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepmind