cs%20to%20box%20out%20competitors%20to%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store%20and%20limited%20users'%20ability%20to%20download%20Android%20apps%20from%20other%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20102%20million%20consumers%20were%20affected%20between%20August%2016%2C%202016%2C%20and%20September%2030%2C%202023%2C%20and%20are%20entitled%20to%20compensation%20of%20at%20least%20%242%2C%20the%20settlement%20agreement%20stipulated.%20Consumers%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-lawsuit-settlement-claim-play-store-apps-payout-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeligible%20for%20the%20Google%20settlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20need%20to%20submit%20any%20sort%20of%20claim%20to%20get%20that%20money%2C%20however.%20Consumers%20will%20receive%20automatic%20payments%20through%20PayPal%20or%20Venmo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260cda2ce-aa92-4537-aa7c-5d8d0b116ea7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle's%20battle%20over%20Europe's%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20be%20forgotten%26quot%3B%20laws%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shadowy%20person%20wearing%20glasses%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blurry%20laptop%20screen%20displaying%20the%20Google%20search%20engine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663beefcb4abc992e8c720a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20lost%20a%20landmark%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20be%20forgotten%26quot%3B%20case%20in%202014%2C%20but%20won%20a%20victory%20in%202019%20when%20an%20EU%20court%20said%20the%20ruling%20was%20limited%20only%20to%20the%20European%20Union.%3Cp%3Epicture%20alliance%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Google's%20biggest%20legal%20battles%20in%20the%202010s%20concerned%20the%20European%20Court%20of%20Justice's%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20be%20forgotten%26quot%3B%20ruling%20and%20whether%20Google%20was%20responsi