ing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusion%20of%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20from%20the%20list%20of%20centrally-contracted%20players%20was%20a%20decision%20that%20was%20solely%20taken%20by%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20has%20revealed%2C%20asserting%20that%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20is%20indispensable%26quot%3B.%20Kishan%20and%20Iyer%20were%20left%20out%20after%20failing%20to%20show%20up%20for%20domestic%20engagements%20despite%20a%20directive%20from%20the%20BCCI.%20While%20Kishan%20went%20on%20a%20long%20break%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20and%20remained%20unavailable%20until%20the%20IPL%2C%20Iyer%20eventually%20did%20feature%20in%20a%20few%20matches%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20including%20the%20semifinal%20and%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Iyer%20still%20found%20himself%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20he%20had%20attended%20a%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20camp%20in%20Mumbai%20when%20his%20domestic%20side%20was%20busy%20playing%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20fixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20check%20the%20constitution.%20I%20am%20just%20a%20convener%20(of%20the%20selection%20meeting)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%20at%20the%20BCCI%20head%20office%20here%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20decision%20lies%20with%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20even%20when%20these%20two%20players%20(Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer)%20who%20did%20not%20play%20domestic%20(cricket)%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20drop%20them%20(from%20the%20central%20contracts%20list)%20was%20only%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20role%20is%20just%20to%20implement.%20And%20we%20have%20got%20new%20players%20(in%20place)%2C%20like%20Sanju%20(Samson).%20Nobody%20is%20indispensable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20reiterated%20the%20Board's%20position%20that%20Indian%20players%20will%20have%20to%20prioritise%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20contract%20snub%2C%20Shah%20had%20stated%20before%20the%20third%20Test%20between%20India%20and%20England%20in%20February%20this%20year%20that%20he%20would%20completely%20back%20the%20chief%20selector's%20decision%20for%20any%20action%20on%20players%20who%20do%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20Indian%20captain%20and%20team%20management's%20requirement%20for%20participation%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20he%20spoke%20with%20the%20players%20after%20their%20exclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20had%20spoken%20with%20them.%20Media%20had%20even%20carried%20the%20reports%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20Hardik%20(Pandya)%20said%20if%20BCCI%20is%20considering%20me%20for%20white-ball%2C%20then%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20play%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20and%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy.%20Any%20player%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20even%20if%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20high%20scores%20in%20this%20year's%20IPL%2C%20Shah%20said%20ultimately%2C%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20who%20is%20playing%20well%20and%20who%2C%20as%20a%20player%2C%20can%20sustain%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20plays%20well%20in%20the%20IPL...%20like%20say%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20he%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20take%20part%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20but%20he%20can%20play%20in%20Mumbai%20Indians%20as%20a%20player.%20There%20he%20can%20play%20in%20a%20relaxed%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Team%20India%2C%20you%20have%20to%20prove%20yourself%2C%20give%20back%20to%20back%20performances.%20The%20one%20who%20can%20handle%20that%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20right%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20revealed%20details%20of%20his%20conversation%20with%20Kishan%2C%20which%20took%20place%20after%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20match%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20did%20not%20advise%20him%20anything.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20friendly%20talk%20that%20he%20should%20do%20well%20and%20I%20speak%20with%20all%20players%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20been%20a%20few%20media%20reports%20mentioning%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20match%20fees%20for%20domestic%20players%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Shah%20said%20there%20is%20no%20such%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20increased%20the%20pay%20anyway%20and%20also%20incentivised%20Test%20cricket.%20We%20had%20increased%20the%20pay%20by%20100%20per%20cent%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715325720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fe6tdqvc8_shreyas-iyer-ishan-kishan-bcci_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkishan-iyers-exclusion-from-central-contracts-was-chief-selector-agarkars-call-jay-shah-5630983%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20left%20out%20after%20failing%20to%20show%20up%20for%20domestic%20engagements%20despite%20a%20directive%20from%20the%20BCCI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Owaisi's%20%26quot%3BYour%20Brother%20Lost%20Amethi%26quot%3B%20Jibe%20To%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20took%20on%20the%20Congress'%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20Thursday%20after%20she%20accused%20the%20Hyderabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20of%20%26quot%3Bworking%20directly%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%26quot%3B%20and%20helping%20the%20ruling%20outfit%20by%20splitting%20votes%20in%20key%20constituencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20shock%202019%20defeat%20-%20he%20lost%20the%20Congress%20bastion%20of%20Amethi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20-%20Mr%20Owaisi%20pointed%20out%20neither%20his%20party%20nor%20he%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20that%20fight.%20He%20also%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20over%20%26quot%3Bnon-secular%20alliances%26quot%3B%20-%20with%20ex-Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20(then%20undivided)%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20he%20linked%20to%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20in%20UP's%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra...%20your%20brother%20lost%20Amethi.%20Did%20I%20come%20and%20fight%20there%3F%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20you%20have%20an%20alliance%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20Is%20he%20secular%3F%20This%20is%20the%20same%20Shiv%20Sena%20whose%20workers%2C%20on%20December%206%2C%20destroyed%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20Are%20you%20with%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20allied%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20Delhi...%20the%20same%20AAP%20that%20helped%20BJP%20remove%20Article%20370%20in%20J%26amp%3BK...%20and%20you%20call%20us%20'BJP%20B-team'%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%20at%20a%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%202019%20election%20you%20lost%2092%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20which%20you%20were%20competing%20against%20the%20BJP.%20This%20time%20you%20are%20fighting%20300%20seats...%20tell%20me%2C%20how%20many%20do%20you%20think%20you%20will%20win%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Owaisi's%20sharp%20response%20came%20after%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20while%20campaigning%20in%20UP's%20Raebareli%2C%20another%20Congress%20bastion%2C%20attacked%20the%20AIMIM%20leader%20for%20working%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5