States%2C%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20tensions%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20terrorism%20in%20different%20geographies%20and%20advent%20of%20new%20technologies%20as%20the%20drivers%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bchurn%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20combination%20of%20all%20of%20this%20today%2C%20poses%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20picture%20of%20great%20churn%2C%20and%20on%20top%20of%20it%20the%20competition%20is%20sharpening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20he%20added%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20voters%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20choose%20wisely%20so%20India%20continues%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20and%20mature%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20choices%20which%20the%20Indian%20voters%20have%20to%20make%20is%20in%20this%20situation%20--%20whom%20do%20you%20trust%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pitching%20for%20continuation%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20has%20a%20massive%20following%20in%20the%20country%20for%20raising%20India's%20and%20the%20Modi%20government's%20profile%20internationally%20with%20his%20hard-nosed%20diplomacy%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20churn%20is%20already%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20you%20have%20a%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20you%20have%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20you%20have%20these%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20you%20have%20tensions%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20you%20have%20terrorism%20in%20different%20geographies%2C%20you%20have%20the%20kind%20of%20problem%20that%20we%20are%20having%20on%20the%20LAC%20(Line%20of%20Actual%20Control)%20with%20China%20but%20other%20countries%20also%20have%20their%20own%20issues%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20United%20States%20is%20diminishing%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20still%20the%20premier%20power%20of%20the%20world.%20But%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20you%20can%20say%2C%20the%20next%20lot%20of%20powers%20are%20so%20much%20closer%20to%20the%20United%20States%20than%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20Also%2C%20the%20US%20itself%20has%20changed%20its%20posture%20vis-a-vis%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20international%20economy%20has%20evolved%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20globalisation%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%20has%20resulted%20in%20concentration%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20technology%20in%20one%20geography%20while%20hollowing%20out%20capacities%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20is%20a%20reaction%20to%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20countries%20across%20the%20globe%20started%20focusing%20on%20having%20more%20centres%20of%20production%2C%20more%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20part%20of%20it%20is%20a%20move%20to%20actually%20diversify%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20the%20second%20is%20because%20of%20the%20hollowing%20out%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20of%20many%20economies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20desire%20today%20to%20protect%20their%20jobs.%20That%20they%20are%20seeing%20the%20social%20consequences%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20a%20very%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20flawed%20model%20of%20globalisation.%20This%20is%20becoming%20a%20very%20big%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20also%20highlighted%20the%20%26quot%3Btremendous%26quot%3B%20impact%20of%20new%20technologies%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20chips%2C%20drones%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20battery%2C%20green%20and%20clean%20technologies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%