siness%2Fchinese-tech-executive-fired-after-endorsing-toxic-work-culture-on-social-media%2Farticleshow%2F110002210.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20First%20Super-Carrier%20Could%20Be%20Indian%20Navy's%20Latest%20Headache%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina's%20first%20super-carrier%20-%20an%2080%2C000%20ton%20warship%20called%20the%20Fujian%20-%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20port%20after%20completing%20its%20brief%20sea%20trial.%20The%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20most%20advanced%20warship%20of%20its%20class%20built%20by%20China%2C%20represents%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20China's%20military%20and%20naval%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fujian%2C%20or%20Type%20003%20class%20carrier%2C%20is%20China's%20first%20indigenous%20aircraft%20carrier%20design%20and%20is%20the%20first%20to%20utilise%20an%20integrated%20propulsion%20system%20and%20electromagnetic%20catapults.%20Electromagnetic%20catapults%2C%20which%20replace%20conventional%20steam-powered%20catapults%2C%20are%20meant%20to%20reliably%20and%20accurately%20launch%20aircraft%20off%20the%20deck%20of%20the%20Fujian.%20The%20US%20Navy%2C%20still%20considered%20the%20world's%20most%20technologically%20advanced%20Navy%2C%20is%20the%20only%20other%20force%20that%20has%20deployed%20this%20technology%20on%20its%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Fujian%20aircraft%20carrier%20features%20a%20new%20integrated%20propulsion%20system%20and%20electromagnetic%20catapults.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Fujian%20aircraft%20carrier%20features%20a%20new%20integrated%20propulsion%20system%20and%20electromagnetic%20catapults.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2gr30m5o_fujian-_625x300_10_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fujian%20aircraft%20carrier%20features%20a%20new%20integrated%20propulsion%20system%20and%20electromagnetic%20catapults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fujian%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20begin%20trials%20of%20its%20carrier-borne%20aircraft%20soon%20which%20could%20last%20up%20to%20a%20year%20before%20the%20warship%20is%20declared%20operational%20in%20all%20respects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20path%20to%20developing%20aircraft%20carriers%20is%20part%20of%20a%20sustained%20effort%20to%20enhance%20its%20naval%20capabilities%20and%20to%20project%20power%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20first%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20Liaoning%2C%20originally%20a%20Soviet-era%20vessel%2C%20was%20purchased%20from%20Ukraine%20in%201998.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20carrier%20was%20incomplete%20and%20was%20lying%20unused.%20It%20was%20subsequently%20refitted%20and%20commissioned%20into%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20Navy%20(PLAN)%20in%202012.%20Liaoning%20has%20primarily%20been%20used%20for%20training%20purposes%20and%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20China's%20growing%20military%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinas%20first%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20Liaoning%2C%20was%20acquired%20from%20Ukraine%20in%201998.%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Chinas%20first%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20Liaoning%2C%20was%20acquired%20from%20Ukraine%20in%201998.%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fqquep77g_liaoning_625x300_10_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20first%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20Liaoning%2C%20was%20acquired%20from%20Ukraine%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shandong%2C%20China's%20second%20carrier%20and%20the%20first%20one%20to%20be%20manufactured%20at%20home%2C%20was%20launched%20in%20April%202017%20and%20entered%20service%20in%20December%202019.%20The%20ship%2C%20a%20significantly%20modernised%20variant%20of%20the%20Liaoning%2C%20has%20seen%20operational%20deployments%20involving%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Shenyang%20J-15%20'Flying%20Shark'%20fighter%2C%20a%20variant%20of%20the%20Russian-designed%20Sukhoi%2033%20fighter%20jet%20that%20incorporates%20significant%20Chinese%20modifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Chinese%20Navy%20is%20developing%20the%20J-35%2C%20a%20carrier-borne%20stealth%20fighter%20that%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20operational%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20J-35%20is%20designed%20to%20operate%20from%20China's%20latest%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20the%20Fujian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20currently%20operates%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20INS%20Vikramaditya%20and%20INS%20Vikrant.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20has%20wanted%20a%20larger%2C%20more%20capable%20aircraft%20carrier%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20only%20to%20be%20rebuffed%20by%20successive%20governments%20concerned%20about%20the%20exorbitant%20cost%20of%20development%2C%20manufacture%20and%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20carrier%20in%20the%20class%20of%20the%20Fujian%20would%20cost%20India%20%247%20billion%20(Rs%2056%2C000%20crore)%20to%20build.%20The%20cost%20of%20new-build%20fighters%20on%20board%20could%20total%20a%20further%20%248%20billion%20(Rs%2065%2C920%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22India%20operates%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20the%20INS%20Vikramaditya%20(in%20the%20distance)%20and%20INS%20Vikrant%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22India%20operates%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20the%20INS%20Vikramaditya%20(in%20the%20distance)%20and%20INS%20Vikrant%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbs07771g_ins-vikramaditya-ins-vikrat_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20operates%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20the%20INS%20Vikramaditya%20(in%20the%20distance)%20and%20INS%20Vikrant%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20green-lighting%20a%20smaller%20carrier%2C%20of%20the%20same-size%20as%20the%20INS%20Vikrant.%20The%20government%20is%20also%20in%20negotiation%20with%20Dassault%20of%20France%20to%20acquire%2026%20Rafale-M%20fighters%20for%20the%20Vikrant%20at%20an%20approximate%20cost%20of%20%248%20billion%20(Rs%2065%2C920%20crore).%20The%20Rafale-M%20would%20replace%20older%20and%20less%20reliable%20Russian-built%20MiG-29K%20jets%20deployed%20on%20board%20the%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20May%202024%2C%20nine%20countries%20operate%20frontline%20aircraft%20carriers.%20These%20countries%20are%20the%20United%20States%2C%20China%2C%20Italy%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20France%2C%20Spain%2C%20and%20Russia.%20The%20United%20States%20leads%20the%20way%20with%2011%20operational%20carriers%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20any%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715324220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhac7a7ro_fujian-_625x300_10_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-first-super-carrier-could-be-indian-navys-latest-headache-5630833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20first%20super-carrier%20-%20an%2080%2C000%20ton%20warship%20called%20the%20Fujian%20-%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20port%20after%20completing%20its%20brief%20sea%20trial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-first-super-carrier-could-be-indian-navys-latest-headache-5630833%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-first-super-carrier-could-be-indian-navys-latest-headache-5630833%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-first-super-carrier-could-be-indian-navys-latest-headache-5630833%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3A%20Will%20Telangana%20Boost%20BJP's%20Tally%20In%20South%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F6rsl3qp8_pm-modi-pti_625x300_03_May_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-launches-projects-worth-rs-7-200-crore-in-telangana-highlights-centres-focus-5179675%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20second%20of%20the%20two%20Telugu-speaking%20states%2C%20heads%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20May%2013%2C%20offering%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-launches-projects-worth-rs-7-200-crore-in-telangana-highlights-centres-focus-5179675%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BJP)%20another%20chance%20to%20send%20representatives%20from%20Southern%20India%20to%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Beyond%20its%20southern%20stronghold%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20an%20impressive%20four%20out%20of%20the%20total%2017%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20was%20achieved%20by%20finishing%20as%20a%20runner-up%20and%20limiting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-blow-to-kcr-chevella-mp-ranjith-reddy-quits-brs-over-current-political-circumstances-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-elections-5255406%5C%22%3Eregional%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BRS%2C%20formerly%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti)%20to%20a%20single-digit%20tally%2C%20thus%20limiting%20the%20party's%20grip%20on%20the%20state%20since%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20setback%20in%20the%20December%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20re-emerged%20as%20the%20principal%20challenger%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20secured%20the%20mandate%20to%20govern%20the%20state%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Conversely%2C%20after%20facing%20rejection%20by%20the%20people%20and%20concluding%20a%20decade-long%20tenure%20in%20office%2C%20the%20BRS%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-780598%5C%22%3EK.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20hoping%20to%20regain%20some%20of%20their%20lost%20prestige%20in%20Telangana.%20Effectively%2C%20the%20contest%20for%20the%2017%20seats%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20triangular%2C%20though%20with%20few%20exceptions%20-%20especially%20the%20high-profile%20Hyderabad%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvantage%20Incumbency%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20December%20assembly%20elections%2C%20faces%20the%20test%20of%20delivering%20and%20raising%20his%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20current%20three.%20The%20Congress%20campaign%20spotlight%20is%20on%20the%20party's%20commitment%20to%20implementing%20the%20five%20guarantees.%20Despite%20financial%20constraints%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20fulfil%20four%20of%20the%20six%20guarantees%20it%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20schemes%20that%20have%20gained%20traction%20is%20the%20free%20bus%20ride%20programme%20for%20women.%20According%20to%20official%20estimates%2C%20approximately%2030%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20avail%20of%20this%20facility%20every%20month%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20estimated%20saving%20of%20Rs%201%2C150%20crore%20for%20women%20since%20the%20scheme's%20implementation%20in%20December.%20The%20free%20bus%20travel%20experience%20may%20also%20be%20expanded%20with%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20promising%20'Nari%20Nyay'%2C%20under%20which%20it%20will%20provide%20Rs%201%20Lakh%20annually%20for%20women%20belonging%20to%20poorer%20sections.%20There%20are%20four%20other%20promises%20on%20offer%3A%20Rs%201%20lakh%20for%20educated%20youth%20through%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20loan%20waiver%20for%20farmers%2C%20Rs%20400%20per%20day%20minimum%20wage%2C%20and%20a%20caste%20census%20for%20better%20targeting%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-kcrs-leaders-swell-congress-bjp-ranks-ahead-of-polls-5361708%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0In%20Telangana%2C%20KCR's%20Leaders%20Swell%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20Ranks%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20limiting%20itself%20to%20mere%20delivery%20and%20promises%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20also%20not%20shied%20away%20from%20fielding%20candidates%20who%20defected%20from%20other%20parties.%20Among%20them%20are%20Ranjit%20Reddy%2C%20Danam%20Nagender%2C%20and%20P.%20Dayakar%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20underwent%20a%20%3Cem%3EGhar%20Wapasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(homecoming).%20Conversely%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20imported%20candidates%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20loss%20of%20momentum%20it%20witnessed%20during%20the%20assembly%20polls%20under%20its%20former%20state%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20striving%20to%20bolster%20its%20national%20campaign%20to%20make%20way%20for%20a%20third%20term%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Unlike%20in%202014%2C%20when%20the%20state%20voted%20as%20a%20single%20entity%20and%20gave%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20nine%20seats%20to%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20BJP's%20objective%20now%20is%20to%20secure%20seats%20in%20double%20digits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20concerted%20effort%20to%20build%20on%20its%20nearly%2020%25%20vote%20share%20in%202019%20has%20seen%20the%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20including%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20dedicating%20time%20to%20campaign%20for%20party%20candidates.%20In%20addition%20to%20emphasising%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20Congress's%20alleged%20favouring%20of%20minorities%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20others%2C%20campaigners%20are%20out%20to%20confront%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EAbki%20Baar%20400-paar%3C%2Fem%3E%20slogan%20signifies%20an%20intention%20to%20alter%20the%20Constitution%20and%20abolish%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2FTribes.%20As%20a%20rebuttal%2C%20the%20campaign%20is%20focusing%20on%20'%3Cem%3EModi%20ki%20Guarantee%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(Modi's%20guarantee)%2C%20highlighting%20how%20welfare%20schemes%20have%20benefited%20all%20without%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRS's%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20former%20chief%20minister%20KCR%2C%20who%20was%20a%20staunch%20advocate%20of%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20present%20an%20opportunity%20to%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20his%20contributions.%20In%20addition%20to%20his%20son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20BRS%20leaders%20are%20working%20to%20energise%20their%20cadres%20even%20as%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20KCR's%20daughter%2C%20remains%20in%20custody%20for%20an%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-remarkable-congress-turnaround-in-telangana-4617796%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20The%20Remarkable%20Congress%20Turnaround%20In%20Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20elections%20come%20just%20five%20months%20after%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%20is%20hoping%20that%20public%20anger%20against%20it%20must%20have%20subsided%20by%20now%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20gradually%20regain%20its%20influence.%20However%2C%20the%20flip%20side%20is%20that%20people%20also%20recognise%20the%20limited%20role%20the%20BRS%20would%20have%20in%20Delhi%20given%20its%20relationships%20with%20the%20two%20key%20national%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cst