timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmasked-man-strangles-woman-with-belt-in-us-drag-body-between-cars-to-sexually-assault-her%2Famp_articleshow%2F109999561.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmasked-man-strangles-woman-with-belt-in-us-drag-body-between-cars-to-sexually-assault-her%2Famp_articleshow%2F109999561.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBear%20Hugs%20Didn't%20Work%26quot%3B%3A%20Biden%20Pulls%20Away%20From%20Netanyahu%20Embrace%20Over%20Rafah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Joe%20Biden%20walked%20onto%20the%20tarmac%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20offered%20a%20warm%20bear%20hug%20to%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20a%20sign%20both%20of%20solid%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20president's%20long%2C%20if%20not%20uncomplicated%2C%20relationship%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20months%20into%20the%20devastating%20conflict%2C%20the%20gentle%20approach%20is%20over.%20Biden%2C%20who%20memorably%20once%20wrote%20to%20Netanyahu%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20for%20the%20first%20time%20raised%20the%20ultimate%20leverage%20the%20United%20States%20has%20on%20Israel%20--%20military%20aid%2C%20which%20totals%20%243%20billion%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20--%20whose%20backing%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20face%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20had%20riled%20the%20left%20of%20his%20Democratic%20Party%20months%20before%20elections%20--%20has%20been%20incensed%20that%20Netanyahu%20has%20rejected%20appeals%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20Rafah%2C%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20city%20where%20the%20United%20Nations%20says%20some%201.4%20million%20displaced%20Palestinians%20are%20sheltering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20administration%20officials%20initially%20saw%20Netanyahu's%20vows%20to%20attack%20Rafah%20as%20rhetorical.%20But%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20including%20a%20visit%20last%20week%20by%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20US%20officials%20have%20been%20convinced%20that%20Netanyahu%20is%20serious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20vowed%20to%20stop%20supplying%20bombs%20and%20artillery%20shells%20if%20Israel%20goes%20ahead%20in%20Rafah%2C%20after%20his%20administration%20confirmed%20it%20had%20already%20halted%20a%20shipment%20of%20thousands%20of%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20who%20last%20spoke%20to%20Netanyahu%20on%20Monday%2C%20has%20made%20his%20case%20on%20Rafah%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20and%20straightforwardly%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20invasion%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Ba%20choice%20that%20Israel%20will%20have%20to%20make.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20we%20hope%20they%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20--%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20which%20carried%20the%20deadliest%20ever%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20--%20publicly%20brushed%20aside%20Biden's%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20alone%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20ambassador%20to%20Washington%2C%20Michael%20Herzog%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bfull%20admiration%26quot%3B%20for%20Biden%2C%20the%20threat%20to%20withhold%20US%20weapons%20was%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsends%20the%20wrong%20message%26quot%3B%20to%20Israel's%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20Republican%20rival%20in%20November%20elections%2C%20former%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20accused%20Biden%20of%20siding%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump's%20relations%20have%20also%20been%20strained%20with%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20swiftly%20recognized%20Biden's%20victory%20in%20the%202020%20election%20which%20Trump%20refused%20to%20concede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAnother%20brawl%20for%20Bibi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFights%20with%20Washington%20are%20familiar%20terrain%20for%20the%20hawkish%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20longest-serving%20prime%20minister%2C%20who%20knows%20the%20United%20States%20intimately%20from%20years%20living%20in%20his%20country's%20primary%20ally%2C%20clashed%20bitterly%20with%20the%20last%20two%20Democratic%20presidents%2C%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Barack%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20openly%20campaigned%20alongside%20Obama's%20Republican%20rivals%20against%20his%20nuclear%20diplomacy%20with%20Iran%2C%20leaving%20lasting%20resentment%20among%20many%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%20as%20Obama's%20vice%20president%20was%20known%20internally%20for%20advocating%20holding%20the%20Israelis%20close%20and%20expressing%20concerns%20privately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20approach%20comes%20both%20from%20his%20history%20with%20Israel%20and%20the%20importance%20he%20attached%20to%20personal%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20often%20spoken%20of%20traveling%20as%20a%20young%20senator%20to%20Israel%20shortly%20after%20the%201973%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%20and%20being%20briefed%20by%20a%20chain-smoking%20prime%20minister%20Golda%20Meir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%202010%20event%2C%20Biden%20said%20his%20father%2C%20horrified%20by%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20said%20his%20love%20of%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20in%20my%20gut%20and%20went%20to%20my%20heart%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20his%20father%20vocally%20supported%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20remarks%2C%20Biden%20described%20Netanyahu%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bclose%2C%20personal%20friend%26quot%3B%20for%20decades%2C%20with%20Biden%20having%20met%20the%20future%20Israeli%20leader%2C%20known%20by%20his%20nickname%20Bibi%2C%20when%20he%20was%20a%20young%20diplomat%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20later%20speech%2C%20Biden%20described%20a%20photograph%20he%20once%20gifted%20to%20Netanyahu%2C%20saying%20he%20inscribed%20on%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BBibi%2C%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20damn%20thing%20you%20say%2C%20but%20I%20love%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'The%20bear-hug%20didn't%20work'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllison%20McManus%2C%20managing%20director%20for%20national%20security%20and%20international%20policy%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20said%20that%20whatever%20the%20two%20leaders'%20history%2C%20their%20interests%20were%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20at%20odds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20personal%20friendship%20that%20is%20somehow%20going%20to%20eclipse%20the%20strong%20political%20interests%20that%20each%20of%20these%20leaders%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20moment%20where%20I%20think%20Biden%20sees%20that%20the%20bear-hug%20didn't%20work.%20The%20strong%2C%20stern%20words%20didn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithholding%20the%20weapons%20is%20the%20biggest%20tool%20of%20influence%20that%20the%20US%20has.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20noted%20that%20Biden%20made%20a%20threat%20rather%20than%20simply%20stopping%20the%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20Biden%20is%20%26quot%3Bleaving%20the%20door%20for%20Netanyahu%20to%20pull%20back%20from%20Rafah%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715322240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F42v9reng_joe-biden-netanyahu-reuters_650x400_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbear-hugs-didnt-work-biden-pulls-away-from-netanyahu-embrace-over-rafah-5630697%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Joe