20finally%20moving%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Palighar%20opened%20its%20gates%20to%20its%20first%20guests.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20homestay%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20happy%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteeped%20in%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalighar%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20homestay%20that%20smells%20of%20customs%20and%20traditions%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20luxury%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20homestay%20gives%20the%20guests%20is%20an%20authentic%20escape%20from%20their%20city%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKabir%20shares%20that%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20noticed%20how%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20area%20were%20being%20modernised.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old-school%20mud%20homes%20with%20sloping%20bamboo%20roofs%2C%20which%20were%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20area%2C%20were%20all%20gone.%20In%20losing%20our%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20traditional%20culture%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20traditional%20technique%20called%20Irka%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20what%20the%20technique%20involves%20is%20using%20bamboo%2C%20wood%20and%20mud%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20The%20mud%2C%20mixed%20with%20dung%20and%20straw%2C%20is%20plastered%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20woven%20with%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Karan%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20made%20mud%20bricks%20which%20are%20baked%20in%20the%20sun.%20We%20used%20the%20land%20from%20our%20own%20property%20which%20helped%20us%20reduce%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%20We%20were%20really%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20on%20the%20nature%20around%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ahana%20also%20points%20out%20that%20another%20reason%20to%20use%20mud%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20coolant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20temperatures%20in%20these%20areas%20have%20typically%20been%20low%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20hotter%20days%20now.%20We%20wanted%20to%20use%20a%20method%20that%20keeps%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally%20which%20is%20why%20we%20used%20mud%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20588px)%20100vw%2C%20588px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%20588w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349522%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20currently%20has%20two%20ensuite%20rooms%20and%20a%20common%20dining%20area.%20The%20property%20is%20located%20on%203.5%20acres%20of%20paddy%20and%20maize%20fields.%20It%20offers%20scenic%20outdoors%20with%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20mountain%20farm%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20multiple%20lawns%20for%20you%20to%20take%20walks%20in%20and%20a%20gazebo-style%20seating%20area%20where%20you%20can%20sip%20delicious%20Darjeeling%20tea%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%2C%20the%20homestay%20also%20follows%20an%20eco-friendly%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20practice.%20We%20encourage%20our%20guests%20not%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20water%20as%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20filtered%20water%20over%20bottled%20water.%20We%20also%20compost%20all%20our%20kitchen%20waste%20and%20leaves.%20This%20compost%20eventually%20goes%20back%20to%20our%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shows%20the%20process%20of%20mulching%20and%20composting%20to%20the%20guests%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20is%20also%20a%20haven%20for%20bird%20watchers%20and%20nature%20lovers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20seven%20years%2C%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20make%20a%20habitat%20for%20butterflies%2C%20insects%20and%20birds.%20We%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20insects%20and%20birds%20flocking%20in%20the%20area%20such%20as%20Rent%20Vented%20Bulbul%2C%20Common%20Tailorbird%2C%20Gray%20Treepie%20etc%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%2048%20hours%20at%20Palighar%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20spending%20your%20time%20admiring%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20cottages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20activities%20that%20you%20can%20indulge%20in%20at%20the%20Palighar%20Homestay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20activities%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20destination%2C%20Palighar%20is%20outside%20the%20town%20area%20of%20Kalimpong.%20The%20guests%20who%20ideally%20come%20and%20stay%20with%20us%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20calm%20vacation%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20guests%20arrive%2C%20the%20couple%20briefs%20them%20about%20the%20property%20and%20the%20surroundings.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20they%20have%20settled%20in%2C%20we%20also%20give%20them%20a%20list%20of%20activities%20that%20we%20do.%20The%20guests%20can%20walk%20with%20us%20and%20trek%20to%20the%20villages%20nearby%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kabir%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20trek%2C%20we%20encourage%20them%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20villagers%20and%20understand%20their%20ways%20of%20living.%20If%20our%20guests%20are%20interested%2C%20we%20also%20explain%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20terrace%20farming%20with%20a%20live%20demonstration.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20guests%20can%20also%20go%20on%20a%20longer%20trek%20to%20River%20Relli%2C%20where%20they%20can%20have%20a%20small%20picnic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20hold%20cooking%20classes%20for%20the%20guests%20who%20want%20to%20cook%20our%20traditional%20dishes.%20The%20dishes%20that%20are%20served%20are%20all%20traditional%20Nepali%2C%20Tibetan%20and%20Bhutanese%20dishes%20used%20with%20ingredients%20from%20our%20farm%20and%20the%20surrounding%20farms%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-6-1-1715264286.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20built%20using%20bamboo%20and%20mud.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A