d%20of%20wire%20fraud%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20conspiracy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sentenced-prison-ftx-alameda-research-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentenced%20to%2025%20years%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20prison%20in%20March%20and%20gave%20his%20first%20in-person%20interview%20from%20MDC%20to%20Puck%20News'%20William%20D.%20Cohan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20published%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20discussed%20his%20conditions%20in%20the%20federal%20prison.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20wrong%20and%20is%20planning%20to%20appeal%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20was%20not%20permitted%20a%20pen%2C%20pad%2C%20recorder%2C%20phone%2C%20or%20watch%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20so%20his%20observations%20were%20subsequently%20written%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20CEO%20of%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2Fexclusive-prison-chat-with-sam-bankman-fried%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Puck%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20subsists%20off%20beans%20and%20bags%20of%20rice%20purchased%20from%20the%20commissary%20and%20that%20his%20rice%20%26quot%3Bhas%20become%20one%20of%20the%20currencies%20of%20the%20realm%20inside%20MDC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%2C%20Cohan%20estimates%2C%20has%20lost%2025%20pounds%20and%20looks%20fitter%2C%20which%20may%20be%20in%20part%20because%20he%20says%20the%20vegan%20food%20he%20is%20served%20is%20inedible%20and%20his%20fellow%20inmates%20told%20him%20it%20smells%20like%20%26quot%3Bshit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20crypto%20mogul%2C%20who%20is%20known%20by%20his%20initials%20SBF%2C%20told%20Puck%20he%20is%20in%20a%20section%20of%20the%20prison%20that%20mainly%20houses%20female%20prisoners%20but%20that%20his%20ward%20is%20a%20large%20room%20with%20bunk%20beds%20that%20holds%2035%20men.%20He