r-personality-change-when-you-speak-another-language-stockholm-university-tlccu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20suggests%20personalities%20can%20change%20when%20you're%20speaking%20another%20language.%20%26quot%3BEnvironmental%20cues%2C%20such%20as%20language%20use%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20adjustments%20in%20mood%20and%20demeanor.%20Multilinguals%20often%20use%20different%20languages%20for%20distinct%20purposes%2C%20and%20those%20purposes%20will%20influence%20your%20emotional%20states%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nateyoung.se%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENate%20Young%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Marie%20Sklodowska-Curie%20Fellow%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oslo%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Young%3C%2Fspan%3E%20holds%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20Linguistics%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0from%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EQueen%20Mary%2C%20University%20of%20London%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20much%20of%20my%20experience%20in%20Spain%20involves%20frustration%20with%20my%20own%20language%20limits%2C%20it's%20shaped%20how%20I%20feel%20when%20speaking%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20this%20is%20what%20some%20refer%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bnodding%20dog%20syndrome.%26quot%3B%20If%20I'm%20tired%20or%20if%20the%20social%20situation%20means%20multiple%20people%20are%20in%20the%20conversation%2C%20I%20end%20up%20nodding%20along%2C%20%26quot%3Bs%C3%AD%2C%20s%C3%AD%26quot%3B%20to%20everything.%20Debating%20something%20complex%20in%20Spanish%20is%20beyond%20my%20language%20level%2C%20but%20I%20also%20know%20I'll%20sound%20rude%20if%20I%20disagree%20using%20the%20blunt%20language%20tools%20I%20do%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdded%20to%20that%20is%20the%20naivete%20that%20comes%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-abroad-europe-love-relationship-lessons