es.%20It%20is%20common%20for%20the%20recruiter%20to%20explain%20all%20the%20steps%20in%20the%20first%20call%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20types%20and%20number%20of%20interviews.%20This%20information%20is%20also%20easily%20accessible%20on%20online%20forums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20list%20of%20technical%20topics%20that%20I%20revise%20a%20week%20before%20the%20interview%20so%20that%20I%20am%20relaxed%20on%20the%20last%20day.%20On%20the%20day%20before%2C%20I%20go%20online%20and%20look%20up%20the%20experiences%20of%20people%20who%20have%20recently%20interviewed%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20I%20am%20applying%20for%20Google%2C%20I'll%20go%20to%20a%20coding%20practice%20website%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleetcode.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeetcode%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20click%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiscuss%26quot%3B%20tab.%20Here%2C%20people%20share%20their%20company-specific%20interview%20experiences.%20I%20look%20at%20what%20popular%20questions%20are%20and%20if%20the%20user%20has%20any%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20pass%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mostly%20use%20it%20as%20a%20checklist%20to%20ensure%20I%20am%20comfortable%20answering%20those%20questions.%20If%20I%20spot%20anything%20new%2C%20I%20look%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20keep%20the%20the%20last%20day%20light%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20stressed%20during%20the%20interview%20or%20even%20the%20day%20before.%20Interviews%20require%20you%20to%20be%20good%20at%20communication%20and%20time%20management%20and%20pressur%3Cs%3Eiz%3C%2Fs%3Eing%20yourself%20on%20the%20last%20day%20might%20cause%20more%20harm%20than%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f32e9dc-a0c8-4cc3-9067-922c4f2dcb96%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20questions%20to%20ask%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20before%20a%20big%20interview%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20planning%20what%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20hiring%20managers%20at%20the%20end%20of%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20step%20is%20important%20for%20not%20only%20doing%20well%20in%20the%20interview%20but%20also%20for%20analyzing%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20ask%20hiring%20managers%20these%20three%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20advice%20do%20they%20have%20for%20someone%20who%20wants%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20has%20their%20growth%20been%20in%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20what%20level%20did%20they%20join%2C%20and%20where%20are%20they%20at%20now%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20do%20my%20research%20on%20the%20company's%20upcoming%20projects%20or%20the%20systems%20they%20use%20and%20bring%20it%20up%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20question.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAnswers%20to%20these%20questions%20give%20me%20more%20information%20about%20the%20company%20and%20play%20a%20role%20in%20my%20decision%20if%20I%20am%20comparing%20multiple%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20question%2C%20if%20someone%20says%20they%20joined%20the%20company%20as%20a%20fresh%20graduate%20and%20moved%20to%20a%20staff%20engineer%20role%20in%20three%20years%2C%20it%20tells%20me%20the%20company%20rewards%20top%20performers.%20I%20try%20to%20ask%20multiple%20people%20this%20question%20and%20look%20for%20a%20pattern.%20A%20few%20people%20saying%20they%20are%20at%20the%20same%20level%20they%20joined%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20makes%20the%20company%20culture%20less%20appealing%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20helping%20me%2C%20these%20questions%20tell%20the%20hiring%20team%20that%20I%20am%20someone%20who%20has%20done%20their%20homework%20about%20the%20company%20and%20is%20interested%20in%20the%20work%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20is%20now%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20interview%20panel%2C%20I%20love%20when%20candidates%20ask%20me%20about%20my%20career%20growth%20in%20the%20company%2C%20or%20specific%20questions%20like%20why%20Meta%20is%20focusing%20on%20AI.%20This%20shows