l%20teacher%20back%20then%20and%20would%20get%20together%20with%20some%20friends%20from%20my%20community%20to%20have%20raving%20discussions%20about%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%20friends%20Juin%20refers%20to%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20teachers%20and%20other%20professionals%20who%20would%20meet%20periodically.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20one%20of%20such%20discussions%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20we%20were%20merely%20talking%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%20beyond%20that.%20As%20we%20were%20a%20bunch%20of%20teachers%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20what%20we%20knew%20best%20%E2%80%94%20teach.%20So%20we%20started%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129899%2Fgoa-construction-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20a%20construction%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20start%20teaching%20kids%20of%20the%20workers%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349408%5