s%20stress%20on%20understanding%20concepts%20deeply%20rather%20than%20just%20memorisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20second%20chance%20at%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20these%20kids%20have%20a%20safe%20place%20here%20to%20thrive%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20their%20lives%20still%20lingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20hail%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20travel%20frequently%2C%20leaving%20their%20children%20under%20my%20care.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20returning%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20these%20children%20confront%20challenges%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20at%20such%20tender%20ages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20a%20distressing%20incident%20during%20their%20summer%20vacation%20when%20she%20encountered%20one%20of%20her%20students%20begging%20on%20the%20streets.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20children%20who%20stay%20with%20us%20leave%20for%20summer%20vacations%20to%20their%20homes.%20While%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20life%20here%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20poverty%20they%20were%20born%20into%20hits%20hard.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20vacation%20days%20that%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20students%20begging.%20It%20was%20heart-wrenching%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20upset.%20I%20spoke%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20the%20mother%20simply%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20will%20they%20eat%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20beg%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Juin%20realised%20the%20stark%20contrast%20the%20children%20experience%20in%20their%20transition%20from%20hostel%20to%20home.%20It%20stressed%20the%20gravity%20of%20her%20work%2C%20as%20it%20dawned%20upon%20her%20that%20good%20education%20serves%20as%20their%20only%20ticket%20to%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20reflecting%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20hunger%2C%20Juin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20young%20boy%20under%20our%20care%20who%20confessed%20that%20chewing%20%3Cem%3Egutka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tobacco)%20helped%20curb%20his%20hunger.%20That%20statement%20shattered%20me.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20begin%20to%20comprehend%20the%20mental%20anguish%20that%20boy%20endured.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20what%20the%20foundation%20aims%20to%20fight.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20about%20educating%20them%20but%20also%20making%20them%20independent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20explains%20that%20once%20the%20children%20are%20prepared%20to%20leave%20Pathshala%2C%20she%20assists%20them%20in%20acquiring%20vocational%20education%20to%20secure%20employment%20or%20gain%20admission%20to%20college%20for%20further%20education.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20only%20way%20we%20can%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20have%20a%20good%20life%20not%20just%20at%20the%20hostel%20but%20beyond%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organization%20follows%20a%20unique%20curriculum%20in%20which%20children%20are%20placed%20in%20different%20grades%20based%20on%20their%20proficiency%20in%20each%20subject.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-3-1715240465-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20follows%20a%20unique%20curriculum%20in%20which%20children%20are%20placed%20in%20different%20grades%20based%20on%20their%20proficiency%20in%20each%20subject.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20also%20informs%20that%20they%20have%20implemented%20Government%20schemes%20%E2%80%98Udyam%E2%80%99%20for%20skill%20development%20training%20and%20%E2%80%98Unnati%E2%80%99%20for%20hands-on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311132%2Fmother-daughter-sustainable-lifestyle-brand-helps-homemakers-earn-bags-shark-tank-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneurial%20training.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20policy%20is%20to%20support%20them%20until%20they%20achieve%20economic%20independence.%20Pathshala%20is%20fundamentally%20a%20value-based%20institution%2C%20dedicated%20to%20nurturing%20children%E2%80%99s%20happiness%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESejal%20Verma%20(21)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20education%20and%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20currently%20working%20part-time%20and%20earning%20enough%20to%20support%20myself.%20I%E2%80%99m%20also%20pursuing%20a%20course%20at%20ITI%20Vadodara.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20this%20would%20have%20