s%2C%20millet%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20candidate%20to%20promote%20both%20health%20and%20sustainability.%20Their%20efforts%20gave%20birth%20to%20%E2%80%98Siri%20Millets%E2%80%99%20in%202017%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20popularise%20the%20grain%20through%20value-added%20products%20like%20snacks%2C%20flakes%2C%20vermicelli%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20they%20were%20about%20to%20launch%20their%20products%20on%20a%20grand%20scale%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20dealt%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20their%20meticulously%20planned%20strategies.%20Yet%2C%20this%20adversity%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20hidden%20blessing%2C%20spurring%20them%20to%20innovate.%20Out%20of%20this%20challenge%20emerged%20the%20idea%20of%20millet-based%20ice%20cream!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20was%20not%20easy%2C%20yet%20they%20persisted%20with%20research%20and%20development%20for%20eight%20months.%20Finally%2C%20their%20labour%20of%20love%2C%20%E2%80%98Siri%20%E2%80%93%20House%20of%20Vegan%20Ice%20Creams%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20launched%20in%202020.%20With%20four%20functional%20outlets%20today%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20expand%20their%20footprint%20through%2010%20to%2015%20stores%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20providing%20a%20vegan%2C%20more%20nutritious%20alternative%20to%20ice%20cream%2C%20they%20are%20also%20working%20on%20educating%20youngsters%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20eating%20habits%20through%20awareness%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20they%20make%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet-based%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20four%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20to%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabu%20(