yours.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20further%20pay%20homage%20to%20Indian%20spices%2C%20Saigal%20shares%20a%20dream%20she%20has%20long%20since%20harboured%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Sauce%20Boss%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20will%20make%20sauces%20easily%20available%20and%20accessible%20for%20people%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20experiences%20that%20influenced%20this%20dream%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20my%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20I%20see%20a%20huge%20variety.%20A%20curry%20in%20North%20India%20is%20different%20from%20one%20in%20South%20India%3B%20a%20curry%20in%20Kolkata%20is%20different%20from%20one%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20on%20the%20western%20coast.%20While%20we%20recognise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348165%2Fcurry-map-of-india-rogan-josh-kadhi-lal-maas-jholi-masor-tenga-besara-pulissery-gushtaba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepth%20of%20flavour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20popular%20opinion%20is%20that%20a%20curry%20is%20complex%20with%20over%2050%20ingredients.%20Through%20Sauce%20Boss%2C%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20versatility%20of%20Indian%20food%2C%20where%20one%20sauce%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20a%20range%20of%20dishes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6Gf27Dr8Ah%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6Gf27Dr8Ah%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%