%20fruit%20or%20vegetable%20to%20grow%2C%20the%20activity%20was%20not%20as%20fruitful%20as%20I%20hoped%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20she%20discovered%20an%20alternative%3A%20growing%20microgreens.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20what%20began%20as%20a%20way%20to%20make%20farming%20more%20engaging%20for%20her%20students%20would%20later%20become%20a%20career%20path%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMicrogreen%20plants%20require%20less%20time%20to%20grow%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20my%20students%20to%20cultivate.%20However%2C%20as%20I%20began%20to%20explore%20them%20further%2C%20I%20realised%20they%20are%20nutrient-dense%20and%20are%20considered%20a%20superfood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Aditi%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Mali%20Greens%2C%20a%20business%20that%20offers%20over%2018%20different%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20to%20more%20than%20900%20customers%20across%20the%20city.%20We%20talked%20to%20her%20extensively%20about%20the%20intricacies%20of%20running%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304873%2Fkerala-man-grows-microgreens-superfood-at-home-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrogreens%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20you%20can%20start%20one%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Entrepreneurship%20is%20in%20my%20blood%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Aditi%20says%20that%20she%20has%20been%20learning%20and%20doing%20marketing%20for%20her%20father%20since%20she%20was%20a%20child.%20%E2%80%9CBusiness%20is%20in%20my%20blood.%20I%20have%20been%20around%20businessmen%20my%20whole%20life.%20However%2C%20as%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20started%20to%20drift%20a%20little%20towards%20other%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20graduation%2C%20she%20opted%20for%20Urban%20Planning%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20way%20villages%20work.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20rural%20lifestyle.%20The%20city%20life%20is%20good%20but%20if%20I%20was%20given%20a%20choice%2C%20I%20would%20have%20lived%20in%20a%20smaller%20city%20or%20farming%20in%20a%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20was%20nurtured%20over%20time%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20study%20urban%20farming%20and%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349306%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20was%20a%20commerce%20student%20in%20school%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20could%20not%20do%20a%20masters%20in%20farming.%20I%20was%20adamant%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20urban%20farming%20which%20is%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20colleges%20outside%20India.%20I%20found%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20got%20admitted%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20went%20beyond%20mere%20farming%3B%20it%20delved%20deeply%20into%20the%20nutrition%20we%20require.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%2C%20I%20began%20teaching%20as%20a%20visiting%20faculty%20member%20at%20several%20colleges%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Watching%20my%20students%20grow%20microgreens%20inspired%20me%20to%20try%20it%20out%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20previously%20her%20work%20and%20life%20got%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20we%20were%20all%20confined%20to%20our%20homes%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20I%20had%20an%20empty%20guest%20room%2C%20which%20I%20converted%20into%20a%20space%20to%20grow%20microgreens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20whole%20process%20very%20intriguing%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20it%20up%20as%20a%20business.%20I%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20my%20own%20farm%20and%20grow%20microgreens%20commercially.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20Mali%20Greens%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20growing%201%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20at%20home%20and%20now%20my%20farm%20can%20grow%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20in%20one%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20microgreens%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalling%20between%20the%20categories%20of%20a%20baby%20green%20and%20a%20sprout%2C%20microgreens%20are%20nutrition-packed%20herbs%20and%20vegetables.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3Earticle%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20often%20contain%20higher%20nutrient%20levels%20than%20more%20mature%20vegetable%20greens.%20This%20makes%20them%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20any%20diet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C