l-24-1715159574-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20believes%20that%20growing%20microgreens%20with%20the%20right%20tools%20and%20guidance%20can%20be%20done%2C%20adding%20that%20you%20can%20simply%20start%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%20of%20growing%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20harvesting%20process%20of%20microgreens%2C%20Aditi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20vertical%20farm%20and%20we%20do%20it%20indoors.%20The%20microgreens%20take%20an%20average%20of%205%20to%207%20days%20to%20grow%2C%20but%20it%20also%20depends%20on%20the%20variety.%20We%20deliver%20them%20according%20to%20the%20demand.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20trials%20and%20errors%2C%20Aditi%20has%20developed%20a%20method.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20chemical-free%20seeds%20to%20grow%20our%20microgreens.%20We%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20very%20organic%20in%20our%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20do%20not%20use%20any%20pesticides.%20On%20day%20one%2C%20we%20grow%20them%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20and%20once%20they%20sprout%2C%20we%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20light%20room.%20We%20harvest%20only%20on%20demand%20to%20reduce%20wastage.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20ensures%20that%20the%20delivery%20is%20fresh%20and%20natural.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20overproduce%20at%20all%2C%20we%20feed%20it%20to%20stray%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.